<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>世界新闻头条、最新国际新闻、世界突发新闻 - 印度时报</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world</link><description>世界新闻：TOI 带来最新的世界新闻头条、《时事国际》全球突发新闻。深入分析和全球头条新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 14:04:48 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>在普京竞选总部，士兵的妻子说带他回家</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/at-putin-campaign-hq-soldiers-wife-says-bring-him-home/articleshow/107015296.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107015296.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周六，一名俄罗斯士兵的妻子在弗拉基米尔·普京总统的选举总部对他从乌克兰回国发出了情感呼吁，这在一个禁止公开批评战争的国家是一种挑衅姿态。 “我的丈夫必须在那里（在乌克兰）。我很想知道他什么时候会发布一项法令，要求我的丈夫必须在家，”玛丽亚·安德烈耶娃在竞选工作人员的注视下说道。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 13:41:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/at-putin-campaign-hq-soldiers-wife-says-bring-him-home/articleshow/107015296.cms</guid></item><item><title>人权观察：巴基斯坦2023年面临最严重经济危机</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistans-economic-crisis-in-2023-a-human-rights-watch-report/articleshow/107014696.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107014696.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;据《黎明报》报道，人权观察组织（HRW）表示，巴基斯坦将在 2023 年面临历史上最严重的经济危机之一，贫困、通货膨胀和失业率飙升，危及数百万人的健康权、食物权和适足生活水平人权观察在周五发布的 740 页《2024 年世界报告》中回顾了 100 多个国家的人权实践，并指出国际货币基金组织 (IMF) 坚持紧缩政策和取消补贴，但没有适当的补偿措施给巴基斯坦的低收入群体带来了额外的困难。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 13:04:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistans-economic-crisis-in-2023-a-human-rights-watch-report/articleshow/107014696.cms</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥总统呼吁民众不顾压力不要支持贩毒集团</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mexican-president-calls-on-civilians-not-to-support-drug-cartels-despite-any-pressure/articleshow/107014577.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107014577.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 12:57:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/mexican-president-calls-on-civilians-not-to-support-drug-cartels-despite-any-pressure/articleshow/107014577.cms</guid></item><item><title>巴基斯坦最高民意调查机构质疑高等法院关于寻求删除民意调查标志案件的言论</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistans-top-poll-body-challenges-high-courts-remarks-on-poll-symbol-case/articleshow/107013321.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107013321.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;巴基斯坦选举委员会（ECP）计划向拉合尔高等法院提出申请，要求删除法院在选举标志案中的言论。 ECP 的决定是在法院批评该委员会和选举官员违法之后做出的。 ECP 的目标是删除这些言论，如果被拒绝，将诉诸更高的论坛。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 11:56:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/pakistan/pakistans-top-poll-body-challenges-high-courts-remarks-on-poll-symbol-case/articleshow/107013321.cms</guid></item><item><title>从自然灾害中恢复是缓慢且官僚的。联邦应急管理局新规则旨在减少繁文缛节</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/simplified-recovery-from-natural-disasters-new-fema-rules/articleshow/107012295.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107012295.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联邦应急管理局新规定允许保险不足的房主申请援助。此前，联邦应急管理局无法帮助保险支出超过该机构上限的房主。现在，房主可以从联邦应急管理局获得资金来弥补差额，解决那些努力从自然灾害中恢复的人们所面临的挑战。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 11:05:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/simplified-recovery-from-natural-disasters-new-fema-rules/articleshow/107012295.cms</guid></item><item><title>斯洛伐克民粹主义总理的盟友正在准备竞选总统</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/peter-pellegrini-ally-of-slovakias-populist-prime-minister-running-for-president/articleshow/107012126.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107012126.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;罗伯特·菲科总理的亲密盟友彼得·佩莱格里尼宣布竞选斯洛伐克总统。第一位女总统祖扎娜·查普托娃决定不再寻求连任。第一轮选举定于3月23日举行。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 10:55:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/peter-pellegrini-ally-of-slovakias-populist-prime-minister-running-for-president/articleshow/107012126.cms</guid></item><item><title>13名学生在中国学校火灾中丧生：报道</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/tragedy-in-china-13-students-killed-in-school-fire/articleshow/107011739.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107011739.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国河南省英才学校宿舍火灾造成 13 名学生死亡。火灾已报告给当地消防部门并被扑灭。一名学生受伤，正在接受治疗。当局正在调查起火原因。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 10:36:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/tragedy-in-china-13-students-killed-in-school-fire/articleshow/107011739.cms</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯检察官寻求对乌克兰战争相关案件的嫌疑人判处长期监禁</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-prosecutors-seek-lengthy-prison-terms-for-suspects-in-war-in-ukraine/articleshow/107010030.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107010030.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;俄罗斯西伯利亚法院判处男子枪杀军官 19 年徒刑；圣彼得堡检察官要求对因咖啡馆爆炸案导致著名军事博主死亡的一名女子判处 28 年徒刑。当局严厉惩罚任何反对普京总统乌克兰战争的人，甚至包括和平抗议者。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 09:10:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/russian-prosecutors-seek-lengthy-prison-terms-for-suspects-in-war-in-ukraine/articleshow/107010030.cms</guid></item><item><title>自10月7日以来，以色列对加沙的袭击造成24,927名巴勒斯坦人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/24927-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-strikes-on-gaza-since-october-7-gaza-health-ministry/articleshow/107009893.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107009893.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;加沙卫生部在周六的一份声明中表示，自10月7日以来，以色列对加沙的袭击已造成24,927名巴勒斯坦人死亡，62,388人受伤。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 09:04:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/24927-palestinians-killed-in-israeli-strikes-on-gaza-since-october-7-gaza-health-ministry/articleshow/107009893.cms</guid></item><item><title>中国两起火灾事故已造成21人死亡</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/21-killed-in-two-fire-accidents-in-china/articleshow/107003450.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107003450.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;中国发生两起火灾，造成 21 人死亡，其中包括学生。河南省英才学校火灾造成13名学生死亡。常州市又发生火灾，造成8人死亡。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 03:35:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/21-killed-in-two-fire-accidents-in-china/articleshow/107003450.cms</guid></item><item><title>掌舵人分歧：以色列领导人在针对哈马斯的战争战略上发生冲突</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-leaders-clash-over-war-strategy-against-hamas-divided-at-the-helm/articleshow/107009089.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107009089.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 08:22:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israeli-leaders-clash-over-war-strategy-against-hamas-divided-at-the-helm/articleshow/107009089.cms</guid></item><item><title>空姐在洗手间偷拍未成年人被拘留</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/american-airlines-flight-attendant-arrested-for-allegedly-recording-minor-girls-in-washroom/articleshow/107007200.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107007200.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;美国航空空乘人员埃斯蒂斯·卡特·汤普森三世 (Estes Carter Thompson III) 因试图秘密拍摄一名 14 岁女乘客如厕而被捕。他还因持有其他四名未成年女性乘客的录音而面临指控。汤普森被指控企图对儿童进行性剥削和持有儿童性虐待图像。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 07:20:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/american-airlines-flight-attendant-arrested-for-allegedly-recording-minor-girls-in-washroom/articleshow/107007200.cms</guid></item><item><title>刚果民主共和国总统将在众人面前宣誓就职</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/dr-congo-president-to-be-sworn-in-for-new-term-before-huge-crowd/articleshow/107006555.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107006555.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;刚果民主共和国总统菲利克斯·齐塞克迪将于周六宣誓就职，开始第二个五年任期。此前，他举行了压倒性的选举，反对派称这次选举是一场骗局，并呼吁举行抗议。齐塞克迪是已故历史反对派人物艾蒂安·齐塞克迪的儿子。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 06:34:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/dr-congo-president-to-be-sworn-in-for-new-term-before-huge-crowd/articleshow/107006555.cms</guid></item><item><title>货机在迈阿密机场起飞后不久紧急迫降</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/emergency-landing-of-cargo-plane-at-miami-airport/articleshow/107006932.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107006932.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 06:52:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/emergency-landing-of-cargo-plane-at-miami-airport/articleshow/107006932.cms</guid></item><item><title>以色列轰炸加沙南部，领导人讨论战后未来</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-bombards-gazas-south-as-leaders-discuss-post-war-future/articleshow/107005380.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107005380.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;周六，以色列升级了对加沙地带南部的袭击，总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡和美国总统乔·拜登讨论了关于巴勒斯坦人战后未来的分歧，这意味着两个盟友之间存在分歧。拜登和内塔尼亚胡自12月23日以来首次进行电话讨论，一天前以色列领导人重申拒绝任何形式的巴勒斯坦主权，导致与以色列在战争中主要盟友的紧张关系升级。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 05:32:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/israel-bombards-gazas-south-as-leaders-discuss-post-war-future/articleshow/107005380.cms</guid></item><item><title>2023年中国向印度公民发放18万张签证</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/1-8-lakh-visas-issued-to-indian-citizens-by-china-in-2023/articleshow/107004110.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107004110.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt; 2023年，中国向印度公民发放了超过18万个签证，为印度公民赴华旅游提供了便利。中国驻印度使馆实施取消网上预约、免录指纹、临时减费等措施便利出行。希望印方尽快恢复中国公民正常签证通道，强调人文交流的重要性。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 04:42:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/1-8-lakh-visas-issued-to-indian-citizens-by-china-in-2023/articleshow/107004110.cms</guid></item><item><title>“伊朗应该向巴基斯坦寻求援助，而不是单方面采取行动”：JUI-F 负责人法兹勒·雷赫曼 (Fazlur Rehman)</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-should-have-sought-assistance-from-pakistan-instead-of-taking-action-unilaterally-juif-chief-fazlur-rehman/articleshow/107003545.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107003545.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;法兹尔伊斯兰组织 (JUI-F) 主席毛拉纳·法兹尔·乌尔·拉赫曼 (Maulana Fazl-ur-Rehman) 周五强调，鉴于跨境入侵和安全问题，采取“积极步骤”解决巴基斯坦和伊朗之间的担忧非常重要。该地区的紧张局势加剧。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 03:44:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-should-have-sought-assistance-from-pakistan-instead-of-taking-action-unilaterally-juif-chief-fazlur-rehman/articleshow/107003545.cms</guid></item><item><title>“伊朗在地区紧张局势升级之际进行防空演习”</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-conducts-air-defense-drill-amid-rising-regional-tensions-state-media/articleshow/107002382.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107002382.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;伊朗周五宣布，已成功使用无人机进行了防空演习，旨在拦截其南部和东南沿海的敌对目标。国营新闻电视台援引伊朗陆军发言人的话说：“伊朗军队已经成功推出了一种新的防空方法，利用无人机拦截和瞄准敌对目标。”</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 03:07:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/iran-conducts-air-defense-drill-amid-rising-regional-tensions-state-media/articleshow/107002382.cms</guid></item><item><title>苏丹一座城市发生种族屠杀，造成多达 15,000 人死亡：联合国报告</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ethnic-killings-in-one-sudan-city-left-up-to-15000-dead-un-report/articleshow/107001989.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107001989.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;联合国报告显示，去年在苏丹西达尔富尔地区朱奈纳发生的种族暴力事件中，准军事快速支援部队 (RSF) 和阿拉伯民兵联盟造成 10,000 至 15,000 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 02:38:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/ethnic-killings-in-one-sudan-city-left-up-to-15000-dead-un-report/articleshow/107001989.cms</guid></item><item><title>为什么伊朗是从加沙到巴基斯坦冲突的共同纽带</title><link>https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-involvement-in-conflicts-from-gaza-to-pakistan/articleshow/107001705.cms</link><description>&lt;img align="left" border="0" hspace="10" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/107001705.cms" style="margin-top: 3px; margin-right: 5px;" /&gt;以色列和加沙地带。也门和红海。黎巴嫩、叙利亚、伊拉克——现在还有巴基斯坦。一系列绵延 2897 公里、涉及各种不可预测的武装行动者和利益的冲突，在每一个爆发点上，都有一个共同点：伊朗。与伊朗的联系部分源于伊朗数十年来通过在西亚各地建立志同道合的民兵来遏制威胁和削弱敌人的努力</description><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 02:04:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/irans-involvement-in-conflicts-from-gaza-to-pakistan/articleshow/107001705.cms</guid></item></channel></rss>